        <Parent_String>plaster of Paris [300014927], gypsum plaster [300014925], plaster by composition or origin [300014923], plaster (composite coating) [300014922], coating by composition or origin [300014908], coating (material) [300014907], materials by function [300014692], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
